<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Login | Blood Donor Nepal</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a209b08554.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/index.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/login-register.css">
</head>

<body>
    <% if (message) { %>
        <div class="toast position-fixed bg-success" id="toast-message" role="alert" aria-live="assertive"
            aria-atomic="true">
            <div class="d-flex">
                <div class="toast-body">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check fa-sm" style="color: #f0f0f0;"></i>
                    <%= message %>
                </div>
                <button type="button" class="btn-close me-2 m-auto" data-bs-dismiss="toast" aria-label="Close"
                    style="color: white;"></button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <% } else { } %>
            <header class="header-section text-center text-light py-5">
                <div class="container">
                    <a class="navbar-brand d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" href="/">
                        <img src="../images/blood-donor.png" alt="logo" width="50" height="50" class="me-2">
                        <span class="logo-text">Blood Donor Nepal</span>
                    </a>
                    <p class="lead mt-3">Connecting blood donors with recipients, saving lives with every drop.</p>
                    <a href="/login" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg mx-2">Login</a>
                    <a href="/register" class="btn btn-light btn-lg mx-2 text-danger">Register</a>
                </div>
            </header>

            <!-- Information Section -->
            <section class="info-section py-5">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row mb-4">
                        <div class="col-md-6 d-flex align-items-center">
                            <img src="../images/mission.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded info-img" alt="Our Mission">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center">
                            <h2 class="mb-3">Our Mission</h2>
                            <p>At Blood Donor Nepal, our mission is to bridge the gap between blood donors and
                                recipients. We strive to ensure timely access to life-saving blood transfusions for
                                those in need. By connecting willing donors with hospitals and patients, we aim to
                                create a reliable and efficient blood donation system that saves lives and promotes the
                                spirit of giving.</p>
                            <p>We believe that every donation counts and that together, we can make a significant impact
                                on the health and well-being of our community. Join us in our mission to save lives, one
                                donation at a time.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row mb-4">
                        <div class="col-md-6 order-md-2 d-flex align-items-center">
                            <img src="../images/community.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded info-img"
                                alt="Join Our Community">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center">
                            <h2 class="mb-3">Join Our Community</h2>
                            <p>Become a part of our growing community of voluntary blood donors. By joining Blood Donor
                                Nepal, you can help us build a strong network of individuals committed to making a
                                difference. Our platform makes it easy to sign up, find donation opportunities, and
                                track your donations.</p>
                            <p>We provide resources and support to ensure a smooth and rewarding donation experience.
                                Whether you are a first-time donor or a seasoned volunteer, your participation is
                                invaluable. Together, we can create a healthier and more connected community.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-6 d-flex align-items-center">
                            <img src="../images/donate.png" class="img-fluid rounded info-img" alt="Donate Blood">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center">
                            <h2 class="mb-3">Donate Blood</h2>
                            <p>Your blood donation can save up to three lives. Blood Donor Nepal provides an easy and
                                efficient way for you to donate blood and make a positive impact. We collaborate with
                                hospitals and clinics to ensure that your donation reaches those who need it most.</p>
                            <p>Donating blood is safe, simple, and takes only a little of your time. Your generosity can
                                give someone a second chance at life. Join us in our mission to alleviate blood scarcity
                                and save lives. Sign up today and be a hero in someoneâ€™s life.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Contact Section -->
            <section class="contact-section bg-light py-5">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <h5>Contact Us</h5>
                            <p><i class="bi bi-geo-alt-fill"></i> Jhapa, Nepal</p>
                            <p><i class="bi bi-envelope-fill"></i> contact@blooddonornepal.org</p>
                            <p><i class="bi bi-phone-fill"></i> +977 9807969039</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <h5>About Us</h5>
                            <p>Blood Donor Nepal, developed by <a href="https://github.com/Nickeshadhikari9"
                                    style="color: red; cursor: pointer;text-decoration: none;" target="_blank">Nickesh
                                    Adhikari</a> in 2024, connects blood donors with those in need. Our mission is to
                                ensure timely access to life-saving blood transfusions by providing a user-friendly
                                platform for donors and recipients. Join us in our mission to alleviate blood scarcity
                                and save lives across Nepal.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
            <script>
                //toast popup
                document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
                    const toastElement = document.getElementById('toast-message');
                    if (toastElement) {
                        const toast = new bootstrap.Toast(toastElement);
                        toast.show();

                        setTimeout(() => {
                            toast.hide();
                        }, 4000);
                        const url = new URL(window.location);
                        url.searchParams.delete('message');
                        window.history.replaceState({}, document.title, url);
                    }
                });
            </script>
</body>

</html>